title: Spa/Hot Tub, Plank-Wood Style Flooring, Spacious Walk-In Closet
posting_body: ['Get ready to be inspired and prepare everyday meals in our kitchens that feature microwaves and have a dishwasher for easy clean up.', 'Apart from our fully-equipped kitchens, our homes also include spacious walk-in closets, washer/dryer sets, built-in computer desks, and a private patio or balcony among other thoughtful additions.', 'Other highlights on our property include a resident clubhouse with conference room and internet caf, fitness center, heated swimming pool with hot tub, and pet wash station.', 'Residents of all ages will find an activity to enjoy, whether it is our nine-hole putting green or our life-size chess or cornhole games.', '-Controlled Access/Gated', '-Microwave', '-Washer/Dryer', '-Spacious Walk-In Closet', '-Cozy Gas Fireplace', '-Plank-Wood Style Flooring', '-Four FREE Electric Car Charging Stations', '-Patio/Balcony', '-Built-In Computer Desk', '-Short Term Lease', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Additional Storage Space Available', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.', 'Contact leasing office for details.']
